---
---
<section class="reveal py-[52.8px] bg-navy-900 text-white relative overflow-hidden">
  <div class="max-w-[1340px] w-full mx-auto px-[10px] relative z-10">
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-end mb-16 gap-6">
      <div class="max-w-2xl">
        <p class="font-nav text-[19.2px] font-semibold tracking-[2.5px] text-gold-400 uppercase mb-3">Our Process</p>
        <h2 class="font-heading text-[52.8px] font-semibold leading-[1.2] mb-6">How We Work</h2>
        <p class="font-body text-[17.6px] leading-[1.5] text-gray-300">A streamlined, transparent process from initial concept to final delivery, ensuring quality at every step.</p>
      </div>
      <a href="/contact-us/" class="bg-gold-400 text-navy-900 hover:bg-gold-500 px-8 py-3.5 rounded-full font-nav text-[14.4px] font-semibold tracking-[2px] transition-all uppercase whitespace-nowrap">
        NEED HELP
      </a>
    </div>
    
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8 lg:gap-12 relative">
      <!-- Connecting Line -->
      <div class="hidden lg:block absolute top-12 left-[12.5%] right-[12.5%] h-0.5 bg-white/20 z-0"></div>
      
      <div class="relative z-10 text-center">
        <div class="w-24 h-24 mx-auto bg-white rounded-full p-5 shadow-xl mb-6 flex items-center justify-center border-4 border-navy-900 group hover:border-gold-400 transition-colors">
          <img src="/images/process/Step-1-1.png" alt="Consultation" class="w-full h-full object-contain" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-heading text-[24px] font-medium leading-[1.2] mb-3">Consultation: Listen, Learn, Deliver</h3>
        <p class="font-body text-[17.6px] leading-[1.5] text-gray-400">We take the time to listen and understand your needs, learning about your brand identity and goals. Our collaborative approach ensures we design sportswear that meets your expectations.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="relative z-10 text-center">
        <div class="w-24 h-24 mx-auto bg-white rounded-full p-5 shadow-xl mb-6 flex items-center justify-center border-4 border-navy-900 group hover:border-gold-400 transition-colors">
          <img src="/images/process/Step-2-1.png" alt="Concept" class="w-full h-full object-contain" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-heading text-[24px] font-medium leading-[1.2] mb-3">Concept: Design with Precision</h3>
        <p class="font-body text-[17.6px] leading-[1.5] text-gray-400">Our experienced designers meticulously craft custom sportswear designs, incorporating your feedback to achieve perfection.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="relative z-10 text-center">
        <div class="w-24 h-24 mx-auto bg-white rounded-full p-5 shadow-xl mb-6 flex items-center justify-center border-4 border-navy-900 group hover:border-gold-400 transition-colors">
          <img src="/images/process/MG_8933-2.png" alt="Production" class="w-full h-full object-cover rounded-full" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-heading text-[24px] font-medium leading-[1.2] mb-3">Production: Uncompromising Quality</h3>
        <p class="font-body text-[17.6px] leading-[1.5] text-gray-400">Our skilled workers pay attention to every detail, using high-quality materials and precise techniques to produce sportswear that reflects excellence and craftsmanship.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="relative z-10 text-center">
        <div class="w-24 h-24 mx-auto bg-white rounded-full p-5 shadow-xl mb-6 flex items-center justify-center border-4 border-navy-900 group hover:border-gold-400 transition-colors">
          <img src="/images/process/MG_8942.png" alt="Delivery" class="w-full h-full object-cover rounded-full" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-heading text-[24px] font-medium leading-[1.2] mb-3">The Final Result: Timely Delivery</h3>
        <p class="font-body text-[17.6px] leading-[1.5] text-gray-400">We prioritize meeting your deadlines, ensuring that your sportswear is delivered on time and ready to make an impact.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-16 max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
      <p class="font-body text-[17.6px] leading-[1.5] text-gray-300">At ICM Factory Direct, our work ethics revolve around understanding your needs and delivering exceptional results. Choose ICM Factory Direct for a collaborative approach that prioritizes understanding your needs, designing to perfection, producing sportswear with meticulous attention to detail, and delivering the final result on time. We are committed to creating sportswear that embodies your brand's identity and exceeds your expectations at every step of the process.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
